headline: Where Will Carnival Stock Be in 5 Years?
summary: Carnival (NYSE: CCL)(NYSE: CUK) stock has made a huge recovery since almost sinking, and every year since its rebound is getting better.  In 2023 it achieved record revenue, and in fiscal 2024 (ended Nov. 30), revenue went even higher, and Carnival returned to profitability.  Let's see where Carnival could be in five years from now.
